          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Is mad honey legal in the <br> Europe, West and Middle East?",
            "subtitle": "",
            "description": "<p>Mad Honey is mostly legal across the whole wide world. Still, it's essential to check with an individual country’s legal rules and regulations regarding its food policies. </p><p>Always purchase it from an authentic and reputable source to ensure it performs transparency about the product’s origin and composition while matching the food regulations. In this article, we will explore the question: is mad honey legal?, and examine the countries where it is permitted.<br/><br/></p>",
            "button_text": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "button_text_2": "",
            "button_link_2": ""
          }
        }
